Project Name      : VehicleGateway
Target Board      : STM32 NUCLEO-G071RB
MCU               : STM32G071RBTx
IDE               : STM32CubeIDE
Generated By      : STM32CubeMX

------------------------------------------------------------
Enabled Peripherals
------------------------------------------------------------

ADC1
USART2
GPIO

------------------------------------------------------------
ADC Channels
------------------------------------------------------------

PA0  -> ADC1_IN0   (Vehicle Speed)
PA1  -> ADC1_IN1   (Engine RPM)
PA4  -> ADC1_IN4   (Fuel Level)

------------------------------------------------------------
Temperature Sensor
------------------------------------------------------------

PB6  -> DS18B20 Data

------------------------------------------------------------
UART
------------------------------------------------------------

USART2_TX -> PA2
USART2_RX -> PA3

Baud Rate : 115200
Data Bits : 8
Parity    : None
Stop Bits : 1

------------------------------------------------------------
Power
------------------------------------------------------------

Board Voltage : 3.3V

